how to transform your element into other.

(1) rotation
functions = rotate, rotateX, rotateY, rotateZ, rotate3d
rotate property

(2) scale = zooming
functions = scale, scaleX, scaleY, scaleZ, scale3d 
scale property 

(3) skew = streching type
function = skew, skewX, skewY 

(4) translate = movement 
function = translate, translateX, translateY, translateZ, translate3d 
translate property 

(5) perspective = view 
function = perspective 
property = perspecitve, perspective-origin

(6) matrix 
matrix, matrix3d



